<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Public Opinion Poll</title>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:wght@600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+Devanagari:wght@500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">

</head>

<body>

<header class="topbar">

<div class="brand">
<span class="brand-mark">◆</span>
<span class="brand-text">Public Votes</span>
</div>

<button
id="themeToggle"
class="theme-toggle"
aria-label="Toggle Theme">
☀
</button>

</header>

<main class="page">

<section class="poll-card">

<p class="eyebrow">
Live Public Poll · Ministry of Education
</p>

<h1 class="question-en">
Should DHARMENDRA PRADHAN Continue as Education Minister?
</h1>

<h2 class="question-hi">
क्या धर्मेन्द्र प्रधान को शिक्षा मंत्री बने रहना चाहिए?
</h2>

<div class="vote-buttons">

<button
id="yesBtn"
class="vote-btn vote-btn--yes">

<span>✓</span>
<span>Yes</span>

</button>

<button
id="noBtn"
class="vote-btn vote-btn--no">

<span>✕</span>
<span>No</span>

</button>

</div>

<p
id="statusMessage"
class="status-message">
</p>

</section>

<section class="results-card">

<div class="results-header">

<h3>Live Results</h3>

<span class="live-dot"></span>

</div>

<div class="results-grid">

<div class="result-stat">

<span
id="totalVotes"
class="result-value">
0
</span>

<span class="result-label">
Total Votes
</span>

</div>

<div class="result-stat result-stat--yes">

<span
id="yesVotes"
class="result-value">
0
</span>

<span class="result-label">
Yes Votes
</span>

</div>

<div class="result-stat result-stat--no">

<span
id="noVotes"
class="result-value">
0
</span>

<span class="result-label">
No Votes
</span>

</div>

</div>

<div class="bar-row">

<div class="bar-label">

<span>Yes</span>

<span id="yesPercentLabel">
0%
</span>

</div>

<div class="bar-track">

<div
id="yesBar"
class="bar-fill bar-fill--yes"
style="width:0%">
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="bar-row">

<div class="bar-label">

<span>No</span>

<span id="noPercentLabel">
0%
</span>

</div>

<div class="bar-track">

<div
id="noBar"
class="bar-fill bar-fill--no"
style="width:0%">
</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

</main>

<footer class="page-footer">

<p>
© 2026 Civic Pulse
</p>

</footer>

<!-- Firebase Script -->
<script type="module" src="script.js"></script>

</body>
</html>
